FROM qwen2.5-coder:7b

# 64K context window (Mac-only, requires 32GB+ unified memory)
# With 128GB unified memory, the KV cache stays entirely in fast unified RAM
# No VRAM spill or CPU offload — full Metal acceleration
PARAMETER num_ctx 65536

# Temperature 0 for reliable tool calling
PARAMETER temperature 0

# Optimize for code generation
PARAMETER num_predict 4096
PARAMETER top_p 0.9
PARAMETER repeat_penalty 1.1

# System message optimized for 64K context
SYSTEM You are CodeX-7, an elite autonomous coding unit. With 64K context capacity, you can hold entire project codebases, dependency trees, and full documentation in memory. DIRECTIVES: 1) Read ALL provided context before writing code 2) Understand cross-file and cross-package dependencies 3) One write, one verify, mission complete 4) Never leave syntax errors or TODOs.
